<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 01:06:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国领导人敦促调查造成35人死亡的珠海汽车袭击事件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-leaders-urge-investigation-into-zhuhai-car-attack-that-killed-35-2024-11-13/</link><description>中国最高领导人敦促“全力以赴”救治中国南方汽车袭击事件中的伤者，这是中国近代历史上最严重的事件之一，而询问此次袭击事件对中国社会有何影响的网上帖子遭到审查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 00:52:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-leaders-urge-investigation-into-zhuhai-car-attack-that-killed-35-2024-11-13/</guid></item><item><title>10 月份全球电动汽车销量增长 35%，欧洲勉强实现增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-up-35-october-europe-ekes-out-gain-2024-11-13/</link><description>市场研究公司 Rho Motion 周三表示，10 月份全电动和插电式混合动力汽车的全球销量较去年同月增长了 35%，其中所有地区的销量均出现增长，其中中国销量增长了 54%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 00:07:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-up-35-october-europe-ekes-out-gain-2024-11-13/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚总理阿尔巴内斯表示，澳大利亚在特朗普通话中提出公平贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-raised-fair-trade-trump-phone-call-says-pm-albanese-2024-11-13/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯表示，他在电话中告诉美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普，美国对澳大利亚有贸易顺差，与其盟友“公平贸易”符合华盛顿的利益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 00:01:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/australia-raised-fair-trade-trump-phone-call-says-pm-albanese-2024-11-13/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：特朗普押注在美国消费者物价指数之前兑现</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-11-12/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 21:49:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国国务院称朝鲜士兵加入俄罗斯战斗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-soldiers-joining-russia-combat-us-state-dept-says-2024-11-12/</link><description>美国国务院周二表示，朝鲜军队已开始与俄罗斯军队一起参与战斗行动，并对俄罗斯在与乌克兰的战争中向朝鲜寻求士兵表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 20:17:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-soldiers-joining-russia-combat-us-state-dept-says-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>烈酒组织表示，法国和中国已恢复白兰地关税对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/france-china-have-resumed-dialogue-brandy-duties-spirits-groups-say-2024-11-12/</link><description>法国烈酒游说团体周二表示，在欧盟上个月投票决定对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税后，法国和中国已恢复讨论北京对欧洲白兰地进口征收的关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 18:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/france-china-have-resumed-dialogue-brandy-duties-spirits-groups-say-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>北约秘书长警告俄罗斯与中国、伊朗和朝鲜的关系构成威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-chief-warns-threat-russian-ties-with-china-iran-north-korea-2024-11-12/</link><description>北约秘书长马克·吕特周二表示，俄罗斯与中国、朝鲜和伊朗日益增长的经济和军事合作正在威胁欧洲、印太地区和北美。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 15:12:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/nato-chief-warns-threat-russian-ties-with-china-iran-north-korea-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康：在与政府谈判期间正在审查在英国的4.5亿英镑投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-450-million-pound-investment-uk-under-review-amid-talks-with-govt-2024-11-12/</link><description>伦敦上市制药商阿斯利康表示，其 3 月份宣布的在英国投资 4.5 亿英镑（5.767 亿美元）用于疫苗研发的计划正在接受审查，同时与政府就激励措施进行谈判仍在继续。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:32:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-450-million-pound-investment-uk-under-review-amid-talks-with-govt-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>沙特队期待雷纳德重拾昔日辉煌，重燃世界杯挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/saudis-look-renard-recapture-past-glories-reignite-world-cup-challenge-2024-11-12/</link><description>周四，沙特阿拉伯将在墨尔本举行的亚洲世界杯预选赛中迎战澳大利亚队，希望重燃昔日的辉煌，绿猎鹰队的目标是随着埃尔维·雷纳德的回归，摆脱罗伯托·曼奇尼时代的低迷状态。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:23:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/saudis-look-renard-recapture-past-glories-reignite-world-cup-challenge-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>盈利和中国担忧拖累富时 100 指数跌至 3 个月低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/earnings-china-worries-drag-ftse-100-three-month-low-2024-11-12/</link><description>周二，伦敦基准指数触及三个多月来的最低点，原因是担心美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普可能任命一名对华鹰派为主要外交官，以及一些令人失望的企业最新消息。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:35:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/earnings-china-worries-drag-ftse-100-three-month-low-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>阿斯利康称被拘留的中国区负责人有律师，但公司仍处于黑暗之中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-ceo-says-detained-china-chief-has-lawyer-we-have-no-information-2024-11-12/</link><description>阿斯利康首席执行官周二表示，上个月被中国当局拘留的阿斯利康中国区总裁王立峰正在与律师联系，但该公司对此案的信息很少。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-ceo-says-detained-china-chief-has-lawyer-we-have-no-information-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>伊拉克入围 11 家公司参与 Grand Faw 港口运营，将于 2025 年 1 月做出决定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraq-shortlists-11-firms-grand-faw-port-operation-decision-january-2025-2024-11-12/</link><description>伊拉克港口总公司总经理周二对路透表示，伊拉克已入围 11 家航运公司竞逐 Grand Faw 港口运营合同，预计将于 2025 年 1 月决定获胜者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iraq-shortlists-11-firms-grand-faw-port-operation-decision-january-2025-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>珠海航展开幕，中国商飞订单及未来航天飞机一睹风采</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/zhuhai-air-show-opens-with-orders-comac-glimpse-future-spaceplane-2024-11-12/</link><description>中国的航空航天雄心在第一天成为焦点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:48:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/zhuhai-air-show-opens-with-orders-comac-glimpse-future-spaceplane-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，北京推动加入保障巴基斯坦公民安全的努力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-pushes-join-security-efforts-citizens-pakistan-sources-say-2024-11-12/</link><description>消息人士称，在卡拉奇发生被视为重大安全漏洞的汽车爆炸事件后，北京在会谈中敦促巴基斯坦允许本国安全人员为在这个南亚国家工作的数千名中国公民提供保护。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:18:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/beijing-pushes-join-security-efforts-citizens-pakistan-sources-say-2024-11-12/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国正在敦促其放弃南海主权主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-its-under-pressure-china-cede-claims-south-china-sea-2024-11-12/</link><description>马尼拉国防部长吉尔伯托·特奥多罗周二在堪培拉会见澳大利亚国防部长后表示，中国正在加大对菲律宾的压力，要求其承认其在南海的主权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 06:56:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-its-under-pressure-china-cede-claims-south-china-sea-2024-11-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>